{"tid":2363592,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"第十三屆香港獨立電影節 賣飛啦 200張","createTime":"2021-01-12T10:13:45.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-22T04:07:47.000Z","uid":6845,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"4a64d13241396e31b284c653b679556654a3ccdd","tid":2363592,"uid":6845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-12T10:13:45.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.hkindieff.hk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkindieff.hk%2F&d=REZNLD6XKc%2F2J9Njm9EJue6cow1LS9WQT%2BeJ8I%2F17x8%3D&h=17f5b6c1\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hkindieff.hk/</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg7-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/s720x720/127243799_3789614744404147_6452273206177814453_o.jpg?_nc_cat=100&amp;ccb=2&amp;_nc_sid=730e14&amp;_nc_ohc=hDU66R0LtbQAX8P-LQe&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg7-1.fna&amp;tp=7&amp;oh=018994033f820ab55bb1188625da6a38&amp;oe=602302D4\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg7-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2Fs720x720%2F127243799_3789614744404147_6452273206177814453_o.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D100%26ccb%3D2%26_nc_sid%3D730e14%26_nc_ohc%3DhDU66R0LtbQAX8P-LQe%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg7-1.fna%26tp%3D7%26oh%3D018994033f820ab55bb1188625da6a38%26oe%3D602302D4&h=c4dbe2f5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg7-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-0/s640x640/137278670_3921797674519186_6844025467677415274_o.jpg?_nc_cat=106&amp;ccb=2&amp;_nc_sid=730e14&amp;_nc_ohc=i48duScniFwAX9g0E7J&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg7-1.fna&amp;tp=7&amp;oh=f93b5f0d579781938769c536ce19d0a4&amp;oe=60218DE6\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg7-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-0%2Fs640x640%2F137278670_3921797674519186_6844025467677415274_o.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D106%26ccb%3D2%26_nc_sid%3D730e14%26_nc_ohc%3Di48duScniFwAX9g0E7J%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg7-1.fna%26tp%3D7%26oh%3Df93b5f0d579781938769c536ce19d0a4%26oe%3D60218DE6&h=b70032bc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg7-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-0/p526x296/136384335_3923342857698001_2456726371821113654_n.jpg?_nc_cat=106&amp;ccb=2&amp;_nc_sid=8bfeb9&amp;_nc_ohc=O1K0YWy_dToAX89lX5f&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg7-1.fna&amp;tp=6&amp;oh=b072812cdc0159649938a7120fd70991&amp;oe=602178FF\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg7-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-0%2Fp526x296%2F136384335_3923342857698001_2456726371821113654_n.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D106%26ccb%3D2%26_nc_sid%3D8bfeb9%26_nc_ohc%3DO1K0YWy_dToAX89lX5f%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg7-1.fna%26tp%3D6%26oh%3Db072812cdc0159649938a7120fd70991%26oe%3D602178FF&h=66c4dca0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有學生飛架<br />\n<br />\n第十三屆香港獨立電影節節目詳情更改告示<br />\nNotice: Updates on The 13th Hong Kong Independent Film Festival Programme<br />\n<br />\n首先，感謝各位觀眾對香港獨立電影節的厚愛，幸好得到您們支持我們才能繼續做下去。原本預計第十三屆香港獨立電影節會在影院中舉行，不過因應疫情，政府宣佈在農曆新年前放寬限聚令的機會不大，故此如常於影院舉行的機會已十分渺茫。然而些微障礙並不會磨滅我們舉辦電影節的熱誠及決心，故此，我們在此宣佈我們會將第十三屆香港獨立電影節的節目轉為網上形式放映，請各位觀眾留意以下兩項節目詳情更改：<br />\n<br />\n1. 大部分電影會以網上放映形式放映。觀眾可以在第十三屆香港獨立電影節POPTICKET 購票頁面中購票每場網上放映設有<span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"purple\">200 </span></span>張門票。當日請在放映開始時間前登入POPTICKET 網頁並等待觀看電影🥸，電影在實時放映完畢後將會下架，請務必在當日準時開啟網頁觀看。<br />\n*注意*：訂票冊子的放映時間表及門票優惠細項已不適用，請以POPTICKET 購票頁面的資訊及下圖的網上放映時間表為準。<br />\n<br />\n購票頁面：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.popticket.hk/hkindieff2021\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.popticket.hk%2Fhkindieff2021&d=REZNLD6XKc%2F2J9Njm9EJue6cow1LS9WQT%2BeJ8I%2F17x8%3D&h=769b34b5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.popticket.hk/hkindieff2021</a><br />\n<br />\n2. 部分單元，包括「獨立焦點－捷克電影新浪潮」單元及部分電影的放映將會順延至戲院開放，請各位細心等候消息。<br />\n<br />\n以上為第十三屆香港獨立電影節節目詳情更改，感謝導演及各位合作伙伴能夠快速應變配合。除了捷克電影新浪潮單元及部分電影外，本次在網上放映的節目亦會儘量在之後安排於戲院上映，請觀眾無需擔心。如有任何疑問，歡迎致電2836 6282或發電郵至hkindieff@yingehi.org查詢，謝謝。"},{"pid":"5002741ec1713ece8120f8cad6a084d5a45401d4","tid":2363592,"uid":6845,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-12T10:20:08.000Z","msg":"買會員更加抵 <br />\n上佢地facebook睇啦<br />\n<a href=\"http